would be inflicted via a shadow ritual, but some monsters are capable of inflicting this, or other similar curses by various means such as touch, on sight, etc.

Normally progression will happen on a day-to-day basis. Passing a Survival check will result in improvement, failure in worsening. Heal and possibly Nature or Arcana checks
can also be attempted.
