Luckily this sort of curse is not too difficult to cure. Simply succeeding at the simple complexity level will cause it to be dispelled, thus many victims simply outlast the
condition and recover in a few days time. A basic ritual exists which will bring a success and remove one failure. Many local NPCs know curatives of this sort, and finding one
could be a simple quest.
