/ONSET Stage 0 begins when the character is cursed. ONSET/
/STAGES
    /STAGE /STAGENAME 0 STAGENAME/ The victim transforms on the night of the full moon. STAGE/
    /STAGE /STAGENAME 1 STAGENAME/ The victim transforms whenever they are in the presence of moonlight. STAGE/
    /STAGE /STAGENAME 2 STAGENAME/ The victim transforms in the presence of moonlight, or when they become bloodied. STAGE/
