TOPIC/
/TOPIC" Poisons "/

Poisons, which herein includes other sorts of toxins, lethal or non-lethal, are substances introduced into the body of the victim in some way, where they act as an 
affliction. They are very similar to diseases and can also be treated using the healing or sometimes arcana knacks. There may be magical means to achieve a cure, as 
with any affliction, but it is common for poisons to have a specific antidote. A wide variety of such poisons exist, and most antidotes are specific to one particular
poison, though often they are formulated from similar or identical virtuous substances. As a rule, poisons are associated with the shadow power source, but there are
some which are different. 

Poisons are also one of the more common types of affliction. While it may require esoteric knowledge to place a curse on someone, brewing up a dose of poison doesn't 
generally require a lot of special knowledge, and there are some fairly common plants and even animals which can be readily acquired for this purpose. Many animals are
themselves poisonous, such as some snakes and such. While none of these are likely to be found lying around the average home knowledge of the more common, though less
effective, types is fairly easy to come by.

In fact, poisons might even be purchased or acquired from certain unsavory individuals, and can be deployed by anyone bold enough to dose a victim. Each type of poison has
its own methods of delivery, which are explained in the description.
/FLEXROW
/FLEXCELL
