While the effects of Red Agony are extremely painful, it is luckily one of the easier of the poisons to create an antidote for, requiring only materials which should be
available in most towns and villages who have a person knowledgeable about healing. That being said, once the antidote is administered the victim will stop progressing to 
higher stages of the affliction, but must still make daily checks until 4 successes have been achieved before the symptoms abate.
